{"tid":1765144,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚 7點打後唔去油尖旺","createTime":"2019-12-01T15:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T16:53:02.000Z","uid":185999,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd8eb31ff884102d56713e6d9bb8ff8abc6d669","tid":1765144,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"2019年 12月 1日<br />\n大批防暴警察於夜晚十時開始無差別截查街坊<br />\n令我深深明白到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咁夜就唔應該出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打邊爐食放題 shopping 都唔係藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n為左唔好辜負佢地維持治安嘅一番好意<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家一齊做個好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每晚 7點打後<br />\n食飯買野去玩請去其他區<br />\n等油尖旺區嘅商戶同居民<br />\n感受下寧靜嘅生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果聖誕新年都一樣咁寧靜就好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a684455d912c12998d9995b167db5980dd6804bd","tid":1765144,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲地方本身好少去 <br />\n由細到大屋企人都叫我唔好點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63022412113622714a5ff42538beb4430475aaab","tid":1765144,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"好市民唔出夜街 努力工作 生活儉樸 拒絕消費"},{"pid":"0f969b056189c82719747fc12a192fe1eb36f1e5","tid":1765144,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a684455d912c12998d9995b167db5980dd6804bd","tid":1765144,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲地方本身好少去 <br />\n由細到大屋企人都叫我唔好點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"好市